---
title: Chicken & Artichoke Cassoulet with Crispy Cheesy Breadcrumbs
description: We’ve taken cassoulet – a traditionally slow-cooked French bean casserole – and made it delicious in 30 minutes. You’ll get the same richness from thyme-roasted tomatoes, caramelized onion, and marinated chicken.
